name: ACM
description: Association for Computing Machinery is a club that helps bring together CS Students and work on fun projects!

name: ACM-W
description: The Association for Computing Machinery's Council of Women welcomes all genders and majors in support of women in computing!

name: UPE Honor Society
description: Upsilon Pi Epsilon is an Honors Society that recognizes academic excellence in Computing and Informatics Disciplines.

name: Cyber Security Club
description: Cyber Security Club is a club for those who are interested in cybersecurity and want to advance their cybersecurity careers.

name: 3D Printing Club
description: The mission of the 3D Printing Club is to give all students, regardless of major or skill level, the opportunity to learn about 3D printing.

name: Rowan Gaming Club
description: The Rowan Gaming Club is the perfect place to meet other Profs and play games togther!

name: Chess Club
description: Our purpose is to enjoy the game of chess while improving ourselves and the community through it.

name: Esports Club
description: Rowan University's very own esports sport club! We have teams for a variety of popular games!

name: Engineers Without Borders
description: EWB is a service organization that offers students the opportunity to solve real-world problems in developing countries and local communities.

name: Out in STEM
description: oSTEM is a national organization that is dedicated to the inclusion and professional development for LGBTQ+ students and workplace professionals.
